{
  "texts": [
    "Grad CAM, LIME, and activation visualisation were used to identify the areas of an image the model utilised for classification.",
    "These visualisation tools proved the robustness of the proposed TL.",
    "• Three orthopaedic surgeons were invited to classify the test set and compare their results with the proposed approach.",
    "Furthermore, the proposed results were compared with those provided by three radiologists [4], demonstrating a significant improvement over the latter.",
    "This section briefly overviews the state-of-the-art methods in the field addressed in our work."
  ]
}